Cyberpunk style: A towering neon-lit fortress in a dark rain-soaked cityscape, with multiple glowing security gates stacked vertically like layers of a digital pagoda. Each gate pulses with different colored energy barriers - cyan, magenta, and electric purple. A lone figure in a sleek hooded jacket stands at the base, their silhouette reflected in wet pavement, facing the ascending layers of access. Holographic lock mechanisms float beside each tier, some open and inviting, others sealed with intricate geometric patterns. Digital rain streams down between the levels, carrying fragments of binary code that dissolve before hitting the ground. The architecture blends brutalist concrete with circuit-board patterns embedded in the walls, glowing faintly. In the distance, more fortress towers pierce the smog-filled sky, each representing different protected domains. The mood is atmospheric and slightly intimidating, emphasizing the hierarchical nature of gaining entry through multiple checkpoints to reach what lies within.
